org.cloudgraph.query.expr

Class DefaultBinaryExpr

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.query.expr.DefaultExpr
      • org.cloudgraph.query.expr.DefaultBinaryExpr
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinaryExpr, Expr, Term
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultLogicalBinaryExpr, DefaultRelationalBinaryExpr, DefaultWildcardBinaryExpr

    public abstract class DefaultBinaryExpr
extends DefaultExpr
implements BinaryExpr
    Contains default functionality for query expressions composed of two parts or terms, including a visitor traversal implementation.
    Since:
    0.5.2
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
